OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a chilly start this
OL,6,Fmorning will be dry with sunny spells.
OL,7,FClouding over this afternoon with some
OL,8,Foccasional rain spreading across
OL,9,FTayside, otherwise remaining dry.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRain will spread south across
OL,12,Fall parts for a time this evening.
OL,13,FThen becoming dry during the early
OL,14,Fhours with clearing skies. Cold with
OL,15,Fsome patchy frost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,18,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,19,Fsome sunny intervals. Rather cold.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
